 total water content needs to include both urea and\n     cholinium\n   • d
 o more NMR at different time points\n3. discuss manuscript draft\n   • Cha
 nu found conferences with July deadlines\n   • ☐ target journal: create to
 p 5\n   • ☑ small items: Williams guide\n   • big items: authorship\, titl
 e\, major findings\, work TBD
